name: The way
description:
The way for all of us is the same: Love those around us.

Be kind to your neighbors.

Share what you have with those in need.

Keep in mind that while it is very easy to point the finger of blame, it is also very easy to look up and realize that we aren't the only ones who have had a rough life.

Instead of spreading gossip and mocking someone, think about what you can do for someone else.

Call that friend that has been on the outs.
